ce of intrinsic scatter in the\nMgas-Tx and Lx-Tx relations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2012 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Sep 2012 18:29:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
