or the kinetic theory, Wigner coordinates + gradient expansion\neasily allow the reproduction of the usual phonon Boltzmann kinetic equation.\nIt is also straightforward to derive phonon-phonon correlation corrections to\nkinetic equations. Kinetic equations lead to hydrodynamic (balance) equations\nand we derived phonon-phonon correlation corrections to the entropy, energy and\nmomentum balance equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2012 08:46:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2013 10:08:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-05"}
